name: Tikky Inu
description: Tikky Inu is the world's first TikTok 2 Earn program that rewards content creators for every video they upload on the world's biggest social media platform. Tikky Inu boasts of a robust infrastructure that is designed to leverage the sheer volume and influencing power of TikTok to fuel its ecosystem. With one billion active users, TikTok is a fertile ground for potential investors. Tikky Inu is committed to tapping into this market and bringing them into our project. The system is simple in theory, a feed/feed symbiosis where we will utilize TikTokers to market our project by incentivizing their efforts to encourage them to do so. The logic is indeed very straightforward, but the results will be astronomical - a persistent juggernaut that will never cease to bring amazing volume for our coin. Tikky Inu's system is powered by a decentralized finance project launched in the Binance Smart Chain (BSC) network and primarily governed by the community of investors who will have a voice in determining the progress of the endeavor. The project itself is led by a highly experienced, extremely motivated and totally devoted team. Each member has been part of multi-million dollar crypto launches in the past. Tikky Inu is 100% safe. Liquidity pool is locked and the team is vouched by the most credible influencers in the scene today.
